    <note>Xu Junping [750]  Ge Shengzhong, WJ, 14.19a-20b (wife, surname Ge(2), who died in 1117 at age 73). Junping identified once in wife's funerary inscription as Andao, which must be his zi. He is not listed in the Jiankang zhi or other sources as a Jiangning Zhiping period jinshi, but the jinshi list for Jiangang (Jiangning) is woefully incomplete. I arbitrarily select 1065 rather than 1067 as the year. For identification of surname Ge(2)'s ancestors see reference in Zhou Linzhi cited below. Lu(5) Bao's [3637] father-in-law (Junping's wife's mingzi has Lu(5) Tang, but offices same as Bao). Lu You, QJ, 32.1b; Zhou Linzhi, WJ, 23.13a; XCB, 456.4a, 467.3b.</note>
